# CODEOWNERS — auto-assigns review on every PR.
#
# Currently the project has a single maintainer, so every path
# routes to one owner. The per-directory entries are kept so adding
# additional owners later is a one-line edit per area instead of a
# whole-file rewrite. Syntax: <pattern> <user1> <user2> …; more
# specific patterns later in the file override earlier ones.
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

